title: Death Vomit - Forging A Legacy  mp3  320k    2014
description:
Death Vomit is a death metal band from Yogyakarta, Indonesia.

Formed in the middle 1995, Death Vomit wrote their own death metal material. After a few demos, they released their debut album Eternally Deprecated (1999). This album was self released (Demented Mind Records), and then was re-released in 2002 under licensed by Extreme Souls Production.

In August 2006, The Prophecy was released through Rottrevore Records.

The latest release, Flames of Hate DVD (2009) on Rottrevore Records, was the first death metal DVD in Indonesia. Following this release Death Vomit played on stage with Behemoth and Psycroptic in Indonesia. Death Vomit more recently signed with Xenophobic Records (Australia).
